contentfulProduct.title: Ultra-Stretch 24/7 Smart Pant

content.value: The most versatile pant ever? Comfy enough for lounging, but smart enough for summer weddings or date-night. The lightweight performance fabric has the subtle texture of a wool dress pant, but feels like your favorite yoga pant. Designed to look clean on the leg in a fit that tapers at the hem and sits neatly on the shoe.
Materials: 63% Polyester / 33% Rayon / 4% Stretch
4-Way Active stretch twill
Spill-proof & Moisture-wicking
Snap font waist & internal drawcord
Internal soft-flex waistband
Hidden zip phone pocket at front
Secure back pockets
Model is 6'2 and wearing a size 32x30

Inseam Guide: For anyone 5’9" & under, we suggest ordering the 28" inseam | For anyone 5’10"–6'1", we suggest ordering the 30" inseam | For anyone 6'1"-6'3", we suggest ordering the 32" inseam | For anyone taller than 6'3", we suggest ordering the 34" inseam
Machine wash cold, inside out with like colors.  Do not use fabric softener.  Only non-chlorine bleach when needed. Tumble dry low, do not iron, do not dry clean.
